::Owlhawk/Rodimus::

Owlhawk turns to looks at Ragnar. To him it seemed it would have been obvious.

&quot;Human? No. My kind are fully functional, living, and thinking mechanical life forms. We are referred to as Cybertronian Transformers.&quot;

As Owlhawk finishes Rodimus walks up to them.

&quot;I&#39;m here, Owlhawk.&quot;

Owlhawk went to attention and saluted.

&quot;Yes Sir! These are the bots errrrr... people who wish to speak with you. Sir.&quot;

&quot;At ease, Owlhawk,&quot; said Rodimus.

Rodimus then looked at Ragnar and Katya. He held out his hand to shake.

&quot;Welcome to our base. My name is Rodimus Prime. I&#39;m the General Commander of the Maximals here.&quot; 

